 (born September 18 1954, in Montreal, Canada) is a prominent American experimental psychologist, cognitive scientist, and popular science writer known for 
<REF ID="1744.2" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="subj-det">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="genitive">his</REFEX>
